headline: M&T Bank extends partnership with NFL Buffalo Bills
summary: M&T Bank, based in Buffalo, New York, has extended its partnership with the NFL team the Buffalo Bills. This is the 40th anniversary since the bank first sponsored the Buffalo Bills, according to a...
